Database Backup Tool

Usage:
  db:backup create [options]     Create a backup of the database
  db:backup export [options]     Export database to SQL file
  db:backup list                 List available backups

Options:
  --output <path>               Output file path
  --include-wal                 Include WAL files in backup
  --json                        Output in JSON format
